# Plan File Location

When creating or updating plan files for this project, store them under:

```text
.cursor/plans/
```

Do not store project plans only in the user-level Cursor plans directory. If a plan already exists outside the repository, copy or move it into `.cursor/plans/` so it stays with the COFFEE project.
